SPRINT 1
🎯 Commander's Intent

Build a modular Retrieval Engine that can be evaluated independently of any LLM.

Why? Because every future sprint depends on this.
Agents, RAG, evaluation, observability... they all assume retrieval is trustworthy.

Deliverable (End of Sprint) By the end, I want you to be able to say:
"Given any document collection and configuration, my engine can retrieve the Top-K chunks and measure its performance."

Scope
Document Ingestor:	Read PDFs into text	Build
Chunker:	Configurable size & overlap	Refactor
Chunk class:	Domain object	Design & Build
Embedding Provider:	Pluggable (Nomic, MiniLM...)	Refactor
Retriever:	Top-K cosine similarity	Refactor
Metrics:	Time each stage	Build